---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="2. Market Benchmarks">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="animate-scale js-anim-ready mb-16">
            <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-pistos-black mb-6 leading-tight">
                Selling <span class="text-pistos-red">Infrastructure</span>,<br>Not Just Processing.
            </h1>
            <div class="bg-pistos-surface border border-pistos-border p-8 rounded border-l-4 border-l-pistos-black mb-12 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-lg text-pistos-black font-medium leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    The UAE business setup market has evolved from <strong>brochure sites</strong> to <strong>utility platforms</strong>. Out of 207 analyzed firms, the top tier is no longer just selling licenses; they have built feature-rich, high-value ecosystems.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed">
                    Market leaders are investing in custom logicâ€”standalone cost calculators, trade name APIs, and deep 150+ page knowledge hubs. To position Pistos effectively, we must understand and match these technological benchmarks while offering a superior, frictionless user experience.
                </p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 tracking-tight pl-2 border-b border-pistos-border pb-4">The Top 5 Market Benchmarks & Their Value Propositions</h2>
        </div>
            
        <div class="space-y-12">
            <!-- Benchmark 1 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 js-anim-ready animate-on-scroll bg-white border border-pistos-border p-6 rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
                <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-start border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-pistos-border pb-4 md:pb-0 md:pr-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-2">
                        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-white bg-pistos-black px-2 py-1 rounded">Interactive Utility</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black">A&A Associate</h3>
                    <a href="https://aaconsultancy.ae" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm flex items-center space-x-1 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black mt-2 font-mono transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3 h-3"></i><span>aaconsultancy.ae</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 pl-0 md:pl-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 opacity-5">
                        <i data-lucide="calculator" class="w-24 h-24 text-pistos-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-pistos-black mb-3 text-lg">Value Prop: Interactive Lead Generation</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        A&A demonstrates high technological competence. Instead of relying on static text, they provide immediate utility. They have built separate subdomains for an advanced <strong>Cost Calculator</strong> (`calc.aaconsultancy.ae`) and a <strong>Trade Name Checker</strong> (`tnc.aaconsultancy.ae`).
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-pistos-surface p-3 rounded border border-pistos-border text-xs text-pistos-black">
                        <strong>Market Reality:</strong> They capture client interest by offering free, high-value tools before the client even speaks to an advisor.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benchmark 2 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 js-anim-ready animate-on-scroll bg-white border border-pistos-border p-6 rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
                <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-start border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-pistos-border pb-4 md:pb-0 md:pr-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-muted mb-2 block">Institutional Giant</span>
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black">HLB HAMT</h3>
                    <a href="https://hlbhamt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm flex items-center space-x-1 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black mt-2 font-mono transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3 h-3"></i><span>hlbhamt.com</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 pl-0 md:pl-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 opacity-5">
                        <i data-lucide="landmark" class="w-24 h-24 text-pistos-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-pistos-black mb-3 text-lg">Value Prop: Massive Corporate Authority</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Ranked in the top 8 global audit networks, their site operates as a 150+ page corporate catalog. They offer everything from Business Setup to exact Tax Audit structuring, selling "Enterprise Safety" to risk-averse clients.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-pistos-surface p-3 rounded border border-pistos-border text-xs text-pistos-black">
                        <strong>Strategic Insight:</strong> Their sheer scale immediately builds unquestionable trust. Pistos can counter this by presenting our ecosystem with a hyper-focused, sharper UI.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benchmark 3 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 js-anim-ready animate-on-scroll bg-white border border-pistos-border p-6 rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
                <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-start border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-pistos-border pb-4 md:pb-0 md:pr-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-muted mb-2 block">The Hybrid Model</span>
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black">The Accountant LLC</h3>
                    <a href="https://theaccountant.ae" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm flex items-center space-x-1 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black mt-2 font-mono transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3 h-3"></i><span>theaccountant.ae</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 pl-0 md:pl-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 opacity-5">
                        <i data-lucide="cloud" class="w-24 h-24 text-pistos-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-pistos-black mb-3 text-lg">Value Prop: Tech-First Financials</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        A direct comparable to the "The One Accountant" synergy. They use massive Xero integration banners to attract modern, tech-savvy entrepreneurs, systematically cross-selling setup services.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-pistos-surface p-3 rounded border border-pistos-border text-xs text-pistos-black">
                        <strong>Strategic Insight:</strong> They currently lead the "Cloud Accounting" narrative. Pistos must articulate our full ecosystem (Setup + Tax + IT) to provide a more compelling offer.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benchmark 4 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 js-anim-ready animate-on-scroll bg-white border border-pistos-border p-6 rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
                <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-start border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-pistos-border pb-4 md:pb-0 md:pr-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-muted mb-2 block">Legacy Integration</span>
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black">Farahat & Co</h3>
                    <a href="https://farahatco.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm flex items-center space-x-1 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black mt-2 font-mono transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3 h-3"></i><span>farahatco.net</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 pl-0 md:pl-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 opacity-5">
                        <i data-lucide="scale" class="w-24 h-24 text-pistos-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-pistos-black mb-3 text-lg">Value Prop: Embedded Legal Authority</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Operating for over 35 years, their site fluidly blends deep legal advisory, HR, and formation services. They embed cost estimate forms deep within their extensive 150+ page structure.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-pistos-surface p-3 rounded border border-pistos-border text-xs text-pistos-black">
                        <strong>Market Reality:</strong> They possess historical dominance and deep SEO roots. Countering this requires Pistos to have flawless technical performance (Core Web Vitals) and modern UX.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benchmark 5 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 js-anim-ready animate-on-scroll bg-white border border-pistos-border p-6 rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
                <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-start border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-pistos-border pb-4 md:pb-0 md:pr-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-muted mb-2 block">FinTech Edge</span>
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black">NEX Consultants</h3>
                    <a href="https://nexconsultants.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm flex items-center space-x-1 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black mt-2 font-mono transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3 h-3"></i><span>nexconsultants.com</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 pl-0 md:pl-6 relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 opacity-5">
                        <i data-lucide="receipt" class="w-24 h-24 text-pistos-black"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-pistos-black mb-3 text-lg">Value Prop: Modern Compliance Focus</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-pistos-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        NEX deliberately pushes their E-Invoicing and IT compliance capabilities alongside traditional setup. They position themselves as technologists ready for upcoming UAE mandates.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-pistos-surface p-3 rounded border border-pistos-border text-xs text-pistos-black">
                        <strong>Strategic Insight:</strong> Positioning as a tech-forward firm attracts modern clients. Pistos can mirror this by highlighting the Mindcom IT infrastructure early in the funnel.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Final Synthesis -->
        <div class="mt-24 bg-pistos-black p-10 rounded text-center js-anim-ready animate-on-scroll-delayed shadow-xl">
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Pistos Synthesis Strategy</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-8 text-white/80 font-mono text-sm md:text-base">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="font-bold text-white mb-1">HLB's Weight</span>
                    <span class="text-xs">(Institutional Look)</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-pistos-red text-2xl">+</span>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="font-bold text-white mb-1">A&A's Logic</span>
                    <span class="text-xs">(Apps > Forms)</span>
                </div>
                <span class="text-pistos-red text-2xl">+</span>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="font-bold text-white mb-1">Astro's Speed</span>
                    <span class="text-xs">(UX Superiority)</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/20">
                <p class="text-lg text-white font-medium">To outmaneuver these benchmarks, we must build a platform that feels like HLB, <br class="hidden md:block">offers the utility of A&A, and loads faster than both.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex justify-between mt-16 mb-32">
            <a href="/" class="group flex items-center space-x-2 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black font-medium transition-colors">
                <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
                <span>Prev: 1. Strategy</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/visuals" class="group flex items-center space-x-2 text-pistos-red hover:text-[#852326] font-medium transition-colors">
                <span>Next: 3. Visual Identity</span>
                <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
